License-file: LICENSE
Author: Jim Apple
Maintainer: http://code.google.com/p/priority-queues/
Build-Type: Simple
Cabal-Version: >=1.2
Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/priority-queues/
Category: Data Structures
data-files: proofs/caseTactic.v proofs/Extract.v proofs/PQSig.v proofs/Bootstrap.v proofs/OrderSig.v proofs/Makefile

